{
  "name": "unify-shot-group-sync-into-a-20260406-1746",
  "idea": "Unify shot group sync into a single usePinnedGroupSync hook that handles both image and video mode updates.\n\n## Current state\n- Image sync: usePinnedGroupSync in usePinnedShotGroups.ts watches ShotsContext, auto-adds/removes clips when shot images change (for groups in mode:'images')\n- Video staleness: useStaleVariants watches Supabase realtime + polls generations table for primary variant changes on individual clips. This is a separate system that doesn't know about shot groups or final videos.\n- Final video data: useShotFinalVideos (called via useFinalVideoAvailable) fetches finalVideoMap from shot_final_videos view, refreshes every 30s\n\n## What to build\nExtend usePinnedGroupSync to also handle video mode:\n- For groups in mode:'video': compare the group's videoAssetKey against finalVideoMap.get(shotId).id\n- If they differ (newer final video exists), surface this as a 'stale video' state on the group\n- Render a badge on the shot group (similar to the stale variant amber badge on clips) indicating 'New video available'\n- Context menu gains 'Update to latest video' option that swaps the video clip's asset to the new final video\n- This replaces the need for useStaleVariants to handle final-video-in-shot-group cases\n\n## Data flow\n- usePinnedGroupSync already receives: data, dataRef, applyEdit, shots, registerGenerationAsset\n- Also needs: finalVideoMap (from useFinalVideoAvailable/useShotFinalVideos)\n- Returns: existing sync behavior + staleShotGroupIds: Set<string> (shot groups with outdated video)\n\n## Key files\n- src/tools/video-editor/hooks/usePinnedShotGroups.ts - extend usePinnedGroupSync\n- src/tools/video-editor/components/TimelineEditor/TimelineEditor.tsx - pass finalVideoMap to sync, wire stale state\n- src/tools/video-editor/components/TimelineEditor/TimelineCanvas.tsx - render stale video badge on groups\n- src/tools/video-editor/components/TimelineEditor/ShotGroupContextMenu.tsx - add 'Update to latest video' action\n- src/tools/video-editor/hooks/useSwitchToFinalVideo.ts - may need an updateToLatestVideo function",
